{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t21-train-1","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"整式的加减","title":"针对训练1：整体思想化简求值","difficulty":3,"tags":["整式","化简求值"],"content":"若 $x + 2y = 5$ 时，代数式 $2x^2 - 4x - 5$ 的值为 7，则 $x^2 - 2x - 2$ 的值为 ______。","steps":[{"title":"整体思想","content":"$2x^2 - 4x - 5 = 2(x^2 - 2x) - 5 = 7$\n\n$2(x^2 - 2x) = 12$\n\n$x^2 - 2x = 6$","formula":""},{"title":"求目标式","content":"$x^2 - 2x - 2 = 6 - 2 = 4$","formula":"\\text{答案：}4"}]},"id":"t21-train-1"},"__N_SSG":true}